Class InternalRegistry

    public class InternalRegistry
extends AbstractApplicationRegistry
implements IDistributedApplicationRegistry
    A simple registry that only registers apps within a single JVM instance. This is primarily intended for debugging, but could be used in across a set of applications all within the same JVM.
    Author:
    dawood
